{{Quote|Don't let 'Quoc's modesty fool you. We didn't just break the Summit Class record; we absolutely destroyed it!|Lt. [[Ma'w'shiye]]|<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>}}
'''Summit Class''' was the name of one of the classes at the [[Galactic Outdoor Survival School/Legends|Galactic Outdoor Survival School]].

Around [[17 BBY/Legends|17 BBY]], the Summit Class became the greatest class ever in the GOSS, managing to get a record in the final trek used as an exam. Warren respected the results and the performance of the Summits. [[10 BBY/Legends|Seven years later]], the [[Twilight Class]] broke the Summits record in more than one day.

Former Summit student [[Lunkar An]], who had since created his own survival academy, felt his ego shaken after that and re-joined GOSS as a student, trying to "redeem" himself.

